<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samasta praśasti sahitaṁ śrīmatu hariśca
<lb n="2" break="no"/>dra dattiya piriyagrahāraṁ bāguḷiya Ai
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vadiṁbaru naṁdana saṁvacharada māgha su <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 10 Ā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>daṁdu purāṇada viṣṇubhaṭṭarige caṁgeyahaḷḷi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yalu manōharadēvara mānyadiṁ teṁka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>lu Erekayi mattaru 2 maṁ hiriya mānyaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gaḷōpādiya naḍasuvaru śrī kalinātha <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 10
</p>

